<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8086604561535547218">Tamera Alexander is a USA Today bestselling author and one of today&apos;s most popular writers in the inspirational historical fiction genre. She and her husband live in Nashville, Tennessee, not far from the Southern mansions that serve as the backdrop for six of her award-winning novels.</span>
  <span id="freeText8086604561535547218" style="display:none">Tamera Alexander is a USA Today bestselling author and one of today's most popular writers in the inspirational historical fiction genre. She and her husband live in Nashville, Tennessee, not far from the Southern mansions that serve as the backdrop for six of her award-winning novels.</span>
